column5: To all who ice fish - check your fishing licences - expires Dec 31!     Don
...and if you have a last name with an apostrophy in it their poor programing won't let you buy online and print a temporary...So you'll have to call in/mail in and wait for your card.
Good point Tracker. I was just thinking of that oddley enough at prison, I mean work today
Whew!  I never even thought of my fishing licence expiring.  Kind of scared me when I read your post. Luckily mine expires in 07.  Tom
*phew* sticker on mine says it expires at the end of 08... please remind me then to renew my license...  ps. getting the 3yr sticker reduces my chance of renewing to 1/3... hehe  cd.
